#Approach:

Sum of Beauty of All Substrings – Brute Force with Frequency Array

Is problem me hume har substring ki beauty nikalni hai
aur sabka total sum return karna hai.

Beauty ka matlab hota hai:
substring me sabse zyada frequency wale character ki frequency
minus
sabse kam frequency wale present character ki frequency.

Approach:
Har index i ko substring ka starting point maan lo.
Ab i se end tak substring extend karte jao using j.

Har naye j par ek frequency array maintain karte hain
jisme current substring ke characters ki count store hoti hai.

Ab current substring ke liye:
maximum frequency nikaalo
minimum non-zero frequency nikaalo
beauty = max - min
aur ise total sum me add kar do.

Important:
Minimum nikalte waqt sirf un characters ko consider karna hai
jo substring me present hain, yani jinki frequency 0 nahi hai.

Is tarah hum saari substrings ka beauty calculate kar lete hain.

Time Complexity: O(n^2 * 26)
Space Complexity: O(26) = O(1)

#Code:

class Solution {

    public int getMax(int[] freq){
        int maxi = Integer.MIN_VALUE;
        int n = freq.length;
        for(int i=0; i<n; i++){
            maxi = Math.max(maxi, freq[i]);
        }
        return maxi;
    }

    public int getMin(int[] freq){
        int mini = Integer.MAX_VALUE;
        int n = freq.length;
        for(int i=0; i<n; i++){
            if(freq[i] != 0){
                mini = Math.min(mini, freq[i]);
            }
        }
        return mini;
    }

    public int beautySum(String s) {
        int sum = 0;
        for(int i=0; i<s.length(); i++){
            int[] freq = new int[26];
            for(int j=i; j<s.length(); j++){
                freq[s.charAt(j) - 'a']++;
                int beauty = getMax(freq) - getMin(freq);
                sum += beauty;
            }
        }
        return sum;
    }
}
